details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: What is going on out there? I knew I couldn't trust a recruit to complete even such a simple training assignment.

details.name: Ruby Dusk Commander
details.text: Alarm! Amber Noon forces just entered our lands!

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: Um, Sir... I think we have been spotted...

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: This is all part of the excercise. Since you got caught, your next objective is to claim that HQ.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Oh, and make use of these Tank and Mobile Infantry units, they may come in handy. Be careful though - if you lose them, they can not be replaced.
Claim the enemy HQ.

details.name: Ruby Dusk Commander
details.text: Amber Noon is taking our positions. Send a message about this to King Ludwig immidiately!

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: Enemy HQ has been captured, Sir!

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Good. All is going according to plan...

details.name: Ruby Dusk Commander
details.text: Alarm! We have lost contact with one of our Towers! Investigate immidiately!

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: Um, Sir... I think we have been spotted...

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: This is all part of the excercise. Since you got caught, your next objective is to claim that HQ.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Oh, and make use of these Tank and Mobile Infantry units, they may come in handy. Be careful though - if you lose them, they can not be replaced.
Claim the enemy HQ.

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: How long do you think we will have to stand guard? It's so hot!

details.name: Infantry #2
details.text: Better shut up or you will get an extra turn!

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: *sigh*
Attention, recruits!

details.name: Infantry #1 and Infantry #2
details.text: Sir Grim! Welcome back!

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: How is your training going?

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: No issues, Sir! A Tank and some motorbikes for Mobile Infantry arrived just in time for vehicle excercises.

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Excellent. Your training objective has been updated. Your performance in capturing military structures was terrible.

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: Oh...

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Your new assignment is to practice it some more by claiming this Tower.

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: But Sir... isn't this tower beyond the border, on the Ruby Dusk territory?

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Are you questioning my orders?

details.name: Infantry #1
details.text: No Sir! I wouldn't dare!

details.name: Warlord Grim
details.text: Then get to it.
Claim the Ruby Dusk Tower.
Defend your HQ.
